      "url": "https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/market-monitor-finds-pjm-wholesale-electricity-markets-competitive-302141385.html",
      "title": "MARKET MONITOR FINDS PJM WHOLESALE ELECTRICITY MARKETS COMPETITIVE",
